ence of hamiltonian dynamic $H$-cycles in $H$-colored multigraphs,\nand as a consequence, we obtain sufficient conditions for the existence of\nproperly colored hamiltonian cycle in edge-colored multigraphs, with at least\n$c\\geq 3$ colors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Mar 2023 02:06:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
