 result of Koh\n\\cite{kwangil} as well as its corrected version \\cite[Chap II, \\S12, Theorem\n12.1]{Ursul} are not true, then we corrected this result in the right way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Mar 2023 10:25:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 08:54:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 09:55:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 19 Mar 2023 09:13:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-21"}
